  "message": "security: override follow-redirects to >=1.15.12 (GHSA-r4q5-vmmm-2653) (#9270)\n\nfollow-redirects <=1.15.11 leaks Custom Authentication Headers to\ncross-domain redirect targets. Add npm override to pin to ^1.15.12+\n(transitively pulled by wait-on -> axios -> follow-redirects).\n\nResolves CodeQL VulnerabilitiesID alert #16.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
